Package int3.team2.website.pantry_loogr.domain

Class EndUser

java.lang.Object
int3.team2.website.pantry_loogr.domain.EndUser
public class EndUser extends Object
EndUser contains all data relating to a specific user. When created the first constructor is used with only the necessary parameters.

      public EndUser(int id, String password, String username, String firstName, String lastName, String email, String city, String stateRegion, String zip, String country, int currentRecipe)
      Constructor that is used when getting users from the database. All values except username, email and password may be null.
      Parameters:
      id - id from the database
      password - password of the user
      username - username of the user
      firstName - firstname of the user
      lastName - lastname of the user
      email - email of the user
      city - city of residence
      stateRegion - stateRegion of residence
      zip - zip code of residence
      country - country of residence
      currentRecipe - the recipe that the User is currently cooking
